results.name: cytochrome o ubiquinol oxidase complex

definition.text: A protein complex that possesses cytochrome o ubiquinol oxidase activity; consists of four polypeptide subunits and associated prosthetic groups.

results.comment: See also the molecular function term 'cytochrome o ubiquinol oxidase activity ; GO:0008827'.
